{
  "title": "Sensitivity Labels for Microsoft 365 Copilot Protection",
  "slug": "lables-for-copilot-protection",
  "categorySlug": "security-compliance",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Sensitivity Labels for Microsoft 365 Copilot Protection</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">How to create Sensitivity Labels to use for Data &amp; More Copilot Privacy Protection</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><hr>\n<h3>Introduction</h3>\n<p>Data &amp; More Copilot Protection works in conjuction with Microsoft Purview to prevent Copilot (or any other AI technology) from accessing items containing privacy data or any other information that shouldn't be consumed by AI.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>As a reminder, Copilot respects the permissions of the user running Copilot and can only access data that user has access to. That said, there are many situations where Copilot shouldn't have access to ALL the data the user has access to. There are also many situations where shared data either isn't or can't be proproperly secured to prevent Copilot from accessing the data.</p>\n<p>In these situations, Purview sensitivity labels can be used to remove the <strong>Copy and extract content (EXTRACT)</strong> permission from the data, which is required by Copilot to access the contents of the item.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>Prerequisites</h3>\n<h4>1. Microsoft License Requirements</h4>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">You must have a Microsoft 365 <strong>E5</strong> license to create the Sensetivtiy lable that prohibits Co Pilot from acces data AND all user must at lesat have a&nbsp;<strong>E3</strong> license that includes Microsoft Information Protection (MIP) capabilities.&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>2. Access to the Microsoft Purview Compliance Portal</h4>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">You must have permissions to access the Microsoft Purview Information Protection portal in Azure.&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>3. Azure Permissions</h4>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Your account must be assigned the necessary permissions in Azure to create and manage sensitivity labels. For this, you must be a member of a group that's granted the <strong>Sensitivity Label Administrator</strong> permission. By default, these roles have that permission:&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 80px;\">- Compliance Data Administrator</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 80px;\">- Organization Management</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 80px;\">- Security Administrator</p>\n<h4>4. Data &amp; More License Requirements</h4>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">You must be licensed for the <strong>Copilot Protection</strong> module of Data &amp; More.&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>5. Data &amp; More Permissions</h4>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Your account must have admin permissions in Data &amp; More to confirm the app registration permissions are set correctly and the labels have been published so the Data &amp; More software can use them.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>Creating the Sensitivity Label</h3>\n<p>To get started, browse to <strong>admin.microsoft.com</strong> and log in. In the left-hand navigation, click on <strong>Show all</strong> to display the Admin centers then click on <strong>Microsoft Purview</strong> to launch the Microsoft Purview portal. In the Microsoft Purview portal, click <strong>Information Protection</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"359\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg?width=670&amp;height=359&amp;name=Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg?width=335&amp;height=180&amp;name=Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg?width=670&amp;height=359&amp;name=Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg?width=1005&amp;height=539&amp;name=Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg?width=1340&amp;height=718&amp;name=Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg?width=1675&amp;height=898&amp;name=Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg?width=2010&amp;height=1077&amp;name=Sensitivity-Labels-Arcticle-01.jpg 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>In the Information Protection screen, click <strong>Sensitivity labels</strong> in the left hand navigation, then click <strong>Create a label</strong> to launch the label creation wizard.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Specify the name, description, and color for the new label. In the example shown, the label is called <strong>Exclude from AI</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-12-50-8114-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Specify the scope for the new label by indicating which items it can be applied to.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-12-16-23-9982-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The key to creating a label for Copilot privacy protection is to specify the permissions applied to labelled items. To configure custom permissions, select the <strong>Control access</strong> option.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-14-26-3841-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Select the <strong>Assign permissions</strong> option to configure the permissions associated with this label.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-38-08-7885-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Use the <strong>Add users or groups</strong> option to select the group (or set of users) to be assigned.</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-49-36-4664-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>When configuring the access control, any combination of users and groups can be used, however, the recommendation is to use a <strong>dynamic Microsoft 365 group</strong>, configured to contain only enabled accounts that have been assigned to humans.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The example shown uses a dynamic Microsoft 365 group called <strong>Active Human Accounts</strong> and here's the selection logic used to set the membership for this group.</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"372\" style=\"width: 670px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=372&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=186&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=372&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=558&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=744&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=930&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1116&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-19-41-4091-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Once a group (or set of users) have been selected, use the <strong>Choose Permissions</strong> option and the Custom profile from the drop-down list to specify the level of permissions. Ensure the <strong>Copy and extract content</strong> permission is left deselected.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-01-56-52-2078-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>When configuring the permissions, any set of permissions can be used, however, the recommendation is to use the same set of permissions as the <strong>Editor</strong> role, excluding the <strong>Copy and extract content</strong> permission.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Once the permissions have been set, confirm the selected group (or set of users) and permissions are displaying properly on the <strong>Assign permissions</strong> screen and click <strong>Save</strong> to apply the change.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-17-15-4857-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Set the auto-labelling for files and email.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-02-48-30-1856-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Microsoft's auto-labelling is extremely inaccurate so the recommendation is to leave auto-labelling disabled and leverage Data &amp; More Copilot readiness to apply the new label to the content that needs it.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Additional protection settings can be assigned if you'd like to apply further protection to items with this label. None of these settings are required to prevent Copilot access to data so they should only be enabled to address additional business requirements or scenarios.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-02-49-2186-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Conduct a final review of the settings and click the <strong>Create label</strong> button.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-04-14-0183-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The new label will now appear in the hierarchy of sensitivity labels. By default, the new label will be crated with the highest sensitivity - be sure to adjust the sensitivity to the appropriate level if you have other labels in your environment.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-30-39-9603-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>Publishing the Sensitivity Label</h3>\n<p>Before the new label can be used it needs to be published. To begin, in the left-hand navigation of the <strong>Purview Information Protection</strong> screen, expand <strong>Policies</strong> and click <strong>Label publishing policies</strong>. This will display the list of publishing policies.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If this is the first label in your environment, a new publishing policy is required. If there are already published labels, the new label can either be added to an existing policy or published through a new policy. If custom settings are required for this label, a different policy is required. If using the same settings, for simplicity, the recommendation is to modify the existing policy.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>To modify an existing policy, select the <strong>Edit policy</strong> action.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-39-24-8292-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Click <strong>Edit</strong> to modify the list of labels to publish and select the newly created label, adding it to the list of labels to be published.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-42-21-0521-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Specify the Admin units if being used. If unsure, leave the <strong>Admin units</strong> set to <strong>Full directory</strong> so Copilot information protection can be used everywhere.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-43-00-3863-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Specify the scope for the label. If unsure, leave the scope set to <strong>User and groups</strong> so Copilot protection is available to everyone.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Configure the Policy settings if being used. If unsure, leave all options deselected - none of these options are required for Copilot protection.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-46-34-7720-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Default labels aren't a required for Copilot protection so, if unsure, leave the <strong>Default label</strong> set to <strong>None</strong> and leave the default settings for email, meetings and calendar events, and Fabric and Power BI content.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"484\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=242&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=484&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=968&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1210&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-03-48-09-6981-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If creating a new policy, provide a Name, then click <strong>Submit</strong> on the <strong>Review and finish</strong> screen to publish the new policy.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>Confirming the Data &amp; More Configuration&nbsp;</h3>\n<p>In Data &amp; More, click your name in the top-right corner and select <strong>Organization Settings</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"452\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=226&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=678&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=904&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1130&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1356&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-00-18-1876-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>In the left-hand navigation, click <strong>App registration</strong>, then click the <strong>edit icon</strong> next to the app registration, and confirm <strong>InformationProtectionPolicy.Read.All (MIP Labels)</strong> has a green check mark next to it.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"452\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=226&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=678&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=904&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1130&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1356&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-02-59-3268-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If the green check mark is missing, the permissions for the app registration need to be updated to include the <strong>InformationProtectionPolicy.Read.All</strong> permission.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>To confirm the new label was published properly, in Data &amp; More, click your name in the top-right corner and select <strong>Settings</strong>. Scroll down to the section called <strong>MIP Labels</strong> and click <strong>Update Labels</strong>. Wait a few minutes then click <strong>Show/Hide Labels</strong>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"452\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png?width=335&amp;height=226&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png?width=670&amp;height=452&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png?width=1005&amp;height=678&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png?width=1340&amp;height=904&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png?width=1675&amp;height=1130&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png?width=2010&amp;height=1356&amp;name=image-png-Aug-11-2025-04-10-59-8864-PM.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The new label is properly published, fully replicated in Azure, and ready for use with Data &amp; More Copilot Protection when you can see it in the list of&nbsp; MIP Labels.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>Now What</h3>\n<p>Data &amp; More Copilot Protection can now be used to identify items that should be excluded from Copilot processing and assign the new label to them.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>For help excluding content from Copilot or for any other functionality related to Data &amp; More Copilot Protection, please reach out to our exceptional Support Team.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
  "sourceUrl": "https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/lables-for-copilot-protection"
}